                  <span class="time-wrapper">
                    <span class="time">July 2022</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="desc">
                  I decide to continue my studies back in Spain at ETSII
                  (Seville) to develop It'sFree.
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <div class="direction-l">
                <div class="flag-wrapper">
                  <span class="flag">It'sFree Starting Point</span>
                  <span class="time-wrapper">
                    <span class="time">May 2022</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="desc">
                  Me and my business partners start working on the idea of
                  It'sFree, learning on the go.
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <div class="direction-r">
                <div class="flag-wrapper">
                  <span class="flag">Start of College</span>
                  <span class="time-wrapper">
                    <span class="time">September 2020</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="desc">
                  Start of my Computer Science studies at EPFL, Lausanne
                  (Switzerland).
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <div class="direction-r">
                <div class="flag-wrapper">
                  <span class="flag">End of High School</span>
                  <span class="time-wrapper">
                    <span class="time">July 2020</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="desc">
                  End of all minor studies, ending up with a High School Diploma
                  and an International Baccalaureate Diploma.
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <div class="direction-l">
                <div class="flag-wrapper">
                  <span class="flag">StartUp Weekend</span>
                  <span class="time-wrapper">
                    <span class="time">July 2018</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="desc">
                  My team earned 3rd place at StartUp Weekend. This experience
                  ignited my passion for innovation and entrepreneurship,
                  reinforcing my dedication to pursue entrepreneurial endeavors.
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <div class="direction-l">
                <div class="flag-wrapper">
                  <span class="flag">StartUp Weekend</span>
                  <span class="time-wrapper">
                    <span class="time">March 2018</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="desc">
                  My team won the public prize at StartUp Weekend Youth with the
                  business idea we developed. This event was the starting point
                  for my passion for innovation and entrepreneurship.
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <div class="direction-r">
                <div class="flag-wrapper">
                  <span id="first-entry" class="flag">
                    First Lego League
                  </span>
                  <span class="time-wrapper">
                    <span class="time">March 2015</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <div class="desc">
                  I participated on the First Lego League, an annual contest
                  where participants solve real-life problems by programming
                  robots to overcome specific challenges. My team managed to
                  obtain first place in Andalucía.
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  )
}

